reviewText: Another great book by Dr Chuck Missler.

This book has left me with more questions than when I started reading it. I will be re-reading this book after mulling over all the scenarios & seeking THE LORD for clarity. I will study those scriptures and seek understanding of these exciting & sometimes terrifying times.
As with all of Chuck Missler's material. It is informative, well researched and worthwhile.  A good addition to any Christian library.
It is the glory of God to conceal a thing;but the honour of kings is to search out a matter.
This is an eye opener to the things which can happen in the near future or in the distance future.

Chuck Missler has struck gold in this series. In each of these books (all under a hundred pages) Chuck shows the prophecy in Revelation, and then shows current world events, and how they could possibly correlate.

  He does a masterful job of allowing the Bible to interpret itself, but also does his best to connect the dots for his readers.
Excellent Book, I would highly recommend it.
a good read if interested in future events.
What a great book.  Well written with lots of information that I did not know.  I am anxious to read about the next horse in the series.
This book and others are recommended to anyone with a thirst for knowledge. Knowledge of God and his Son are as necessary as eating.

Enlightening view of scriptures and our current technological abilities. Recommended reading. Why not five stars? The first two chapters are a repeat (annoyingly) of the first book in the series The White Horse.
